      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i need help writing an email to a customer. they bought a really expensive espresso machine from us but it's been stuck in shipping for two weeks now because of a mistake in our warehouse logistics. i need to apologize and sound professional but also keep them happy so they don't cancel the order. can you give me a draft?",
