      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Apology and Update on Your Espresso Machine Order\n\nDear [Customer's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to extend my sincerest apologies for the delay in the delivery of your recently purchased espresso machine. We understand how important it is for you to receive your order promptly, and we regret the inconvenience caused by the unexpected hiccup in our warehouse logistics.\n\nOur team has been working tirelessly to resolve the issue, and I can assure you that your espresso machine is now on its way to you. We are committed to making this right and ensuring that you receive your purchase as soon as possible. As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we would like to offer you a complimentary coffee subscription for the next three months, so you can enjoy the fruits of your investment while we work to resolve this matter.\n\nThank you for your understanding and continued support. We value your business and look forward to serving you in the future.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
